"This displays the &kde; Development Platform version and other basic "
"information."
msgstr "See näitab &kde; arendusplatvormi versiooni ja muud põhiteavet."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thanks and Acknowledgments"
msgstr "Autorid ja litsents"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Special thanks to an anonymous Google Code-In 2011 participant for writing "
"much of this documentation."
msgstr ""
"Eriline tänu suure osa materjali kirjutamise eest kuulub ühele Google'i Code-"
"In 2011 anonüümsele osavõtjale."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:1307
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Levinumad kiirklahvid"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &plasma-workspaces; provide keyboard shortcuts that allow you to perform "
"many tasks without touching your mouse. If you use your keyboard frequently, "
"using these can save you lots of time."
msgstr ""
"&plasma-workspaces; pakuvad klaviatuuri klahvikombinatsioone ehk kiirklahve, "
"mille abil saab mitmeid ülesandeid sooritada ilma hiirt kasutamata. Kui oled "
"aktiivne klaviatuuri kasutaja, võivad kiirklahvid säästa tublisti aega."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This list contains the most common shortcuts supported by the workspace "
"itself and many applications available within. Every application also "
"provides its own shortcuts, so be sure to check their manuals for a "
"comprehensive listing."
msgstr ""
"Allpool on ära toodud mõned levinumad kiirklahvid, mida kasutab töötsoon ise "
"ja paljud selles töötavad rakendused. Kõik rakendused pakuvad ka omaenda "
"kiirklahve, mistõttu tasub neist korraliku ülevaate saamiseks alati uurida "
"vastava rakenduse käsiraamatut."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <keysym>Meta</keysym> key described below is a generic name for the "
"custom key found on many different keyboards. On keyboards designed for "
"&Microsoft; &Windows;, this key is usually called the <keysym>Windows</"
"keysym> key, and will have a picture of the &Windows; logo. On keyboards "
"designed for &Mac; computers, this key is known as the <keysym>Command</"
"keysym> key and will have a picture of the <trademark class=\"registered"
"\">Apple</trademark> logo and/or the <keycap>⌘</keycap> symbol. On keyboards "
"designed for &UNIX; systems, this key is really known as the <keysym>Meta</"
"keysym> key and is typically labeled with a diamond: <keycap>◆</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Allpool mainitav klahv <keysym>Meta</keysym> tähistab üldistatult paljudel "
"klaviatuuridel leiduvat muuteklahvi. Klaviatuuridel, mis on loodud "
"&Microsoft; &Windows; silmas pidades, nimetatakse seda tavaliselt "
"<keysym>Windows</keysym>i-klahviks ning sel on &Windows; logo. "
"Klaviatuuridel, mis on loodud &Mac; arvuteid silmas pidades, tuntakse seda "
"<keysym>Command</keysym>-klahvina ning sel on <trademark class=\"registered"
"\">Apple</trademark> logi ja/või sümbol <keycap>⌘</keycap>. Klaviatuuridel, "
"mis on loodud &UNIX; süsteeme silmas pidades, nimetataksegi seda klahvi "
"<keysym>Meta</keysym>-klahviks ning sel on tavaliselt peal romb <keycap>◆</"
"keycap>."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:1332
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Windows"
msgstr "Akende kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These shortcuts allow you to perform all kinds of operations with windows, "
